messages.message: The … means it’s not returned from TDF.
Please pass the file and query to @Lalit and @Prashant Kikani to take a look
Yes, @Yatharth Vardan can you share the file and prompt here?

I'm seeing this output in when I try your prompt, which is the 1st table on the sheet. (Can you check if you have enabled "Object detection" from the project settings @Yatharth Vardan)

Based on the prompt, I think you're looking to extract the 2nd table in the sheet, which is not supported as of now. We only support 1 table per sheet. As of now, you can try moving that table to a new sheet and try to extract.
This limitation of 1 table per sheet will be removed in the future releases.
